WEBVTT

00:03:56.020 --> 00:04:01.050
false ideas about human beings
will not go away

00:04:01.060 --> 00:04:03.480
if people believe that they're true.

00:04:04.230 --> 00:04:07.100
Because if people believe
that they're true,

00:04:07.110 --> 00:04:10.150
they create ways of living
and institutions

00:04:10.160 --> 00:04:14.010
that are consistent
with these very false ideas.

00:04:14.020 --> 00:04:18.040
And that's how the industrial revolution
created a factory system

00:04:18.050 --> 00:04:22.190
in which there was really nothing you
could possibly get out of your day's work,

00:04:22.200 --> 00:04:25.070
except for the pay at the end of the day.

00:04:25.080 --> 00:04:27.070
Because the father --
one of the fathers

00:04:27.070 --> 00:04:29.120
of the Industrial Revolution,
Adam Smith --

00:04:29.130 --> 00:04:33.100
was convinced that human beings
were by their very natures lazy,